dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2023. [The address point feature class was created to assist 911 dispatchers / calltakers in locating wireless E911 callers. Sources include: current aerial photography, NAIP aerial mosaic imagery, parcel maps, limited GPS collection and physical verification when necessary.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
